# This directory holds offline vendor resources for white-label builds.
# Contents (added during release packaging, NOT committed to git):
# - bin/uv.exe          (uv package manager)
# - git/                (PortableGit for Windows)
# - node/               (Node.js runtime)
# - tools/rg.exe        (ripgrep)
# - tools/ffmpeg.exe    (ffmpeg)
# - hermes-agent/       (repo source snapshot)
# - python/             (Python 3.11 interpreter)
# - site-packages/      (Python dependencies)
# - venv-scripts/       (venv Scripts directory)
# - nm/                 (node_modules, renamed to avoid electron-builder stripping)
# - chromium/           (Playwright Chromium browser)
